## pinctrl-names

**Value type:** `<stringlist>`

A list of strings providing names for the pin control states indexed by `pinctrl-N` properties. The first string names state 0 (`pinctrl-0`), the second names state 1 (`pinctrl-1`), and so on. The string `"default"` conventionally names the active/operational state.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
uart7: serial@880000 {
    pinctrl-names = "default", "sleep";
    pinctrl-0 = <&qup_uart7_default>;
    pinctrl-1 = <&qup_uart7_sleep>;
};
```
